config ZMK_INPUT_PROCESSOR_GRID_MATRIX
    bool "ZMK Input Processor - Trackpad to 3x3 Grid Layer Controller"
    help
      Enables an input processor that converts trackpad absolute coordinate
      events into a 3x3 grid layer controller. Maps each grid cell to a
      ZMK layer (Layers 6-14).
      
      The processor divides the 0-1024 coordinate space into a 3x3 matrix,
      detecting touch by coordinate presence. It uses an 80ms watchdog timer
      to simulate finger lift and deactivate layers.

